  "Description": {
    "English": "An exclusive <span class=\"name name-stellar\">Exosuit Appearance Override</span>.<br><br>A localized anomaly within the jetpack's core allows the spectral afterglow of the <span class=\"name name-special\">boundary horrors</span> to leak across into this reality.<br><br>Transform the appearance of your Exosuit at an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Appearance Modifier</span>.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "一件专属<span class=\"name name-stellar\">套装外观</span>。<br><br>储存在喷气背包核心中的局部异象将使原本属于<span class=\"name name-special\">边界惧物</span>的灵异余晖渗透进这个现实。<br><br>可以在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外观修改器</span>使用以更改你的套装外观。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "獨特的<span class=\"name name-stellar\">強化套裝外觀覆寫</span>。<br><br>噴射背包核心內的局部異常會讓<span class=\"name name-special\">邊界懼獸</span>的光譜餘輝滲透進這個現實。<br><br>在<span class=\"name name-technology\">外觀改造器</span>改變你的強化套裝外觀。"
  },
